<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        @media (max-width:900px){
           .mainDiv{
               width: 80%!important;
               padding: 4%!important;
           }
        }
     </style>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;">
    <div
      style="display: flex; align-items: center; height: 100vh; width: 100%;background-color: rgb(243, 241, 241);"
    >
      <div class="mainDiv"
        style="width: 45%;border-top: 5px solid #3DC0DF; margin: auto; padding: 2%;background-color: white;border-radius: 20px;"
      >
        <div style="font-size: 17px;">
          <h1 style="text-align: center;">REJECTION</h1>
          <div style="line-height: 25px">
            <p>Dear <%= content.userName %>,</p>
            <p>
                Thank you for expressing interest and applies in <%= content.companyName %>. While we were impressed with your qualifications, unfortunately, we’ve decided to move forward with other applicants whose skills and experience better meet our needs at this time.
            </p>
            <p>
                We sincerely appreciate your interest in <%= content.companyName %> and hope that you’ll stay in touch. Please don’t hesitate to reach out if we have another open role that interests you.
            </p>
            <p>
                We wish you the bestin your future endeavors!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding-bottom: 2%;padding-top: 2%;">
            <p>Regards,</p>
            <p>Kritta Patel from <%= content.companyName %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>